  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><strong>Way of Lightning:</strong> 18th level</em></p>\n<p>You can increase the power of your simpler lightning force powers. When you cast a force power of 1st through 6th level that deals lightning damage, you can deal maximum damage with that power.</p>\n<p>You can use this feature with no adverse effects a number of times equal to your Wisdom or Charisma modifier (your choice, a minimum of once). If you use this feature beyond this before you finish a long rest, you take [[/r 2d12]] true damage for each level of the power, immediately after you cast it. Each time you use this feature again before finishing a long rest, the damage increases by [[/r 1d12]].</p>",
